{
  "name": "Commanding Aura",
  "type": "feature",
  "img": "icons/sundries/flags/banner-standard-tattered-red.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You’re surrounded by a 5 Space Aura. You can target any creature within your Aura to grant one of the following effects below, provided the target can see or hear you.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Bolster: (1 AP)</strong> You take the <strong>Help</strong> to aid the target with an Attack. You can also do so as a <strong>Reaction</strong> whenever a valid target makes an Attack.</p></li><li><p><strong>Rally: (1 AP)</strong> You grant creatures of your choice (including yourself) <strong>1 Temp HP</strong>.</p></li><li><p><strong>Reinforce: (1 AP)</strong> When a creature in your aura is targeted by an Attack, you can impose <strong>DisADV</strong> on the Attack against the creature as a <strong>Reaction</strong>.</p></li></ul>",
